item.title: Which Edwards sister was the more effective hitter?
item.description: Taylor Edwards and Tristen Edwards. Two sisters who have both played softball at Nebraska and left their names in the record books. Both have proven their power with their bats. However, I wanted to see which sister was more effective as a hitter. Let’s start with answering the most basic question: who did better career-wise? The first thing I need to do is add the libraries and data I’m going to use.
